channel.title: Ip logging onto completely different server! help now, please fix
channel.description:

This seems like the same thing that happened with obituary.no-ip.biz logging onto "firexfold scape".
Please respond immediately I just want to get back to magic training on rune-revolution.no-ip.biz.
Thank you for your time.
(sorry for making your eyes bleed)
Status: FRUITLESS IN WORKING.
